<br>
So my question to you my fellow Magius is.....  Is there a SOLO CAmp that is Ultra Safe and  I guess that means Ultra BOring Too ( hehe ) , That has Really really Good EXP to Get me Through 52 and maybe even 53 ?<br>
<br>
(please dont say Ice Giants, looking for something different. They can be considered plan B unless everybody thinks the IG's are Plan A ! )<br>
<br>
Im open to all forms of Suggestions.  Please Post as Much info as you can.  Your assistance is greatly apreciated.<br>
