<br>
..|* *|.<br>
..|* *|.<br>
..|* *|.<br>
./.......\<br>
|*|=|*|<br>
<br>
Those 8 can be single pulled.  The next things you have to deal with are two static spawns at the end of the small hallway(one warrior and one crusader) and a wandering crusader.  The wandering crusader wanders all the way up to the stairs, so be careful of him.  After these two statics and the wanderer, there are two more mobs to kill before the dropoff, one golem and one crusader.  The golem can be pulled solo with malosi at 54, possibly at 53 as well I don't remember for sure.<br>
<br>
In my experience everything but the golem is pretty resistant to both fire and magic. The golem is resistant, but less so than the normal elementals.   <p><hr align="left"  width="100%">

