<br>
Run through Kael to WL.  Once in WL turn left and run along the Kael wall (heading North).  You will pass a number a giants along the way, standing against the wall.  Con these, hopefully they still blue.  Run right up into the North corner along the wall.<br>
<br>
There is one roaming sentry that comes into the corner, so wait until he passes on his rounds, then drop invis, bring up a pet, and buf up.  <br>
<br>
Wait for the sentry to come back and slay him.  <br>
<br>
Now you work your way down the wall towards the Kael entrance.  Just pull each wall guard back to your pet.  They are spaced apart enough that you should always single pull.  <br>
<br>
Been ages since I was here, but think the respawn time was 18 mins.  Depending on equipment, KEI, and the like you may get all the way down the wall, or decide to run back to the corner and wait for the roamer (who pops at the south end of the wall, so you will see him coming).<br>
<br>
Loot is nothing, maybe a sword and a few plat.  XP was decent when I did them (but cant remember if I was 50 yet or not.  so long ago).<br>
<br>
these also give CoV faction<br>
