 like it.<br>
<br>
I prefer the NW and SE camps as the other wandering mobs are less likely to jump you at either one. Camps 1 and 5 on the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqatlas.com/luclin/tenebrousmtnsmap.html" target="top">EQAtlas map</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
pull camp 1 from the south side. I can get 4 or 5 single pulls usually.  If you get Bedlavar - put the pet on him and burn him hard.. he HURTS.<br>
<br>
Pull camp 5 from NE side, and above (you'll see what I mean) and pull him up to the zone wall. There is a named here as well, but I cannot remember the name, as I learned with Bedlavar how NOT to get him. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
